strings: <voice_0x01000D7A><se_low>*: Red told me to get the 'orse out for ya before ya got 'ere.
<voice_0x01000D7B><se_low>*: Looks like she knew you'd come up wiv the goods. She must rate ya.
<voice_0x01000D7C><se_low>King Trode: Medea! What a terrible ordeal you must have been through! I'm so sorry! I won't leave you alone again!

<voice_0x01000D7D><se_low>King Trode: I'll never go to the pub like that again!
I promise!
<voice_0x01000D7F><se_low>King Trode: Well, we're ready to leave whenever you are, <most_heroic>. What's our next destination?

<voice_0x01000D80><se_low>Yangus: How about tryin' Brains again?
Maybe the old geezer'll be around to give us some intelligents this time.

<voice_0x01000D82><se_low>Yangus: We've gotta find out where Dhoulmagus is.
Otherwise we'll just be wand'rin' 'round like 'eadless chickens.

<voice_0x01000D83><se_low>King Trode: Hmph. It would be no hardship to me if I
never ever set foot in Pickham again.
But I suppose we have no choice.
